[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Summary of Root Cause  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The compilation failure arises because `BruteForceParser`’s new static constant [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   private static final long MAX_SEARCH_LENGTH = COSParser.DEFAULT_TRAIL_BYTECOUNT;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   attempts to reference a private constant [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`DEFAULT_TRAIL_BYTECOUNT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`COSParser`. We must expose the necessary values [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe trailing‐buffer size and file[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m via public accessors rather than exposing private constants directly.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Preserve Critical Logic  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We still want to preserve the existing backward‐search logic in [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BruteForceParser` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault to `MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET` if the PDF is tiny; [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39motherwise seek no further back than the trailing‐buffer size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must preserve the original `readTrailBytes` behavior in `COSParser`, since [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdownstream parsing and healing rely on that instance field.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Fuzz‐harness and tests expect no changes to public APIs beyond the new [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgetters, and no change to harness or test code.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Patch Steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In `COSParser.java` [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/COSParser.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - After the declaration of the private field  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        private int readTrailBytes = DEFAULT_TRAIL_BYTECOUNT;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        add two public getter methods:  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         * @return the length of the underlying PDF file, for bounded searches.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        public long [0m[1;35mgetFileLen[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            return fileLen;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         * @return the number of trailing bytes scanned when looking for EOF [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmarkers.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         *         This corresponds to the internal DEFAULT_TRAIL_BYTECOUNT.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        public int [0m[1;35mgetEOFLookupRange[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            return readTrailBytes;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - These methods expose both `fileLen` and the trailing‐buffer size without [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maltering access modifiers of existing private members or constants.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In `BruteForceParser.java` [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BruteForceParser.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Remove the static constant that references the private field:  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```diff[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         -    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         -     * Maximum number of bytes to scan backwards from end-of-file[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         -     * when looking for markers.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         -     * Uses default trailing buffer size from COSParser.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         -     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         -    private static final long MAX_SEARCH_LENGTH = [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCOSParser.DEFAULT_TRAIL_BYTECOUNT;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Modify the `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForLastEOFMarker[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method to use the new accessors:  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```java[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         private long [0m[1;35mbfSearchForLastEOFMarker[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             long lastEOFMarker = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             long originOffset = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Determine start offset: either the minimum or bounded by the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrailing buffer.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-            [0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            long fileLen = [0m[1;35mparser.getFileLen[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            int lookupRange = [0m[1;35mparser.getEOFLookupRange[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            long start = fileLen > [0m[1;39m([0m[39mMINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET + lookupRange[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                         ? fileLen - lookupRange[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                         : MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstart[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             long tempMarker = [0m[1;35mfindString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mEOF_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtempMarker != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[33m...[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m restore position, etc.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This removes any illegal reference to private members and uses only public [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification and Benefits  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We maintain full backward‐search bounding, preserving the existing [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET` fallback for very small files.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By exposing `readTrailBytes` via `[0m[1;35mgetEOFLookupRange[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, we do not leak the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate constant, yet provide exactly the same behavior.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introducing `[0m[1;35mgetFileLen[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready added in the last patch attempt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrequired to compute the search offset. Both getters are public and explicitly [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdocumented.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness code or fuzzing logic is modified; all existing tests and public [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAPIs remain compatible.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach adheres to encapsulation: internal constants stay private, yet [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexternal classes can still obtain the runtime values they need.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects and Mitigations  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The only new public APIs are two getters. These can be safely backported to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdownstream code if needed.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No existing functionality is removed or altered.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Edge cases [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPDF shorter than `lookupRange + MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m still seek[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto `MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET`, consistent with pre-patch behavior.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
